    <ul>
      <li>Well, obviously. For the hands on portion of this exercise, you don‚Äôt need it‚Ä¶ but you should install Git anyway if you don‚Äôt have it.</li>
      <li>Windows users: Git comes with Git Bash, a Linux-style command prompt (aka ‚Äúshell‚Äù aka ‚Äúterminal‚Äù), which will make life easier.</li>
    </ul>
